snippet.title: Necken Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Necken is a roguelite set in the Swedish forest. Battle animals and creatures from Nordic folk lore to reach the influential water spirit Necken. Will he grant you a wish or will he lure you into the dangerous water?

-----Necken is available here-----
Website: https://neckengame.com/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/985510/Necken/
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/necken/257078
Itch: https://joccish.itch.io/necken

-----Additional Credits-----
Music: Paul Zimmermann
Voice Acting: Scalefin
Vocals: Orla Conway
